data.description: Discover southern charm & the ultimate Lowcountry lifestyle in established Royal Oak. The private road flanked by mossy live oaks leads you to this 2017 custom built home on 6.26 glorious acres! This marsh front property backs to the tidal creek, boasting its own sparkling pond! Surrounded by serene woods, this sub dividable lot offers spectacular 360 views! Sip sweet tea while rocking on your Carolina porch or relax with an evening cocktail & watch the sea birds from the spacious screened porch! Enjoy fireside marsh front chats from the fire pit seating area. Boasting 4 garage spaces (2 attached & 2 detached) & a long driveway for overflow parking, storage options are endless! Bring your boat or RV! Featuring dual owners' suites, one of which makes the perfect mother-in-law quarters,find two additional main floor bedrooms (one of which is currently set up as a workshop, but owners are happy to remove cabinetry & return it to its original condition). The designer kitchen is the show stopper! Offering a huge island with countertop seating, gas cooking & amazing upgrades, you'll never want to leave! The home also features separate dining & a designated office. Main level owners' suite provides outside access to the screened porch & yard. The focal fireplace is the centerpiece of the open floor plan. Shopping & dining at Freshfields Village, to include a nice grocery, is less than 10 miles away! Beach access at Beachwalker Park at Kiawah Island is just 20 minutes from the home. You'll also be just a few miles from plenty of restaurants, bars & live entertainment at nearby establishments. Properties like this are rarely available, so don't miss your opportunity to live the quintessential coastal life on Johns Island!
